{
  "manifest_version": 3,
  "name": "랭크프리 — 네이버 쇼핑·플레이스 분석",
  "version": "0.3.13",
  "description": "네이버 마케팅을 위한 무료 분석 도구 — 쇼핑·플레이스·키워드·블로그·상품 리뷰를 한 곳에서 분석. 사장님·마케터·셀러가 내 순위와 시장을 빠르게 파악하도록 돕습니다. rankfree.kr 무료 로그인.",
  "icons": {
    "16": "icons/icon16.png",
    "48": "icons/icon48.png",
    "128": "icons/icon128.png"
  },
  "permissions": ["storage", "tabs"],
  "host_permissions": [
    "https://rankfree.kr/*",
    "https://*.rankfree.co.kr/*",
    "http://127.0.0.1:8000/*",
    "http://localhost:8000/*",
    "https://search.shopping.naver.com/*",
    "https://search.naver.com/*",
    "https://m.search.naver.com/*",
    "https://s.search.naver.com/*",
    "https://smartstore.naver.com/*",
    "https://brand.naver.com/*",
    "https://shopping.naver.com/*",
    "https://map.naver.com/*",
    "https://pcmap.place.naver.com/*"
  ],
  "background": {
    "service_worker": "background.js"
  },
  "content_scripts": [
    {
      "matches": ["https://search.shopping.naver.com/search/*"],
      "js": ["content/injected.js"],
      "world": "MAIN",
      "run_at": "document_start"
    },
    {
      "matches": ["https://search.shopping.naver.com/search/*"],
      "js": ["content/content.js", "content/shop-seo.js"],
      "css": ["content/panel.css", "content/seller-power.css", "content/shop-seo.css"],
      "run_at": "document_idle"
    },
    {
      "comment": "관리자 화면 ↔ 확장 브릿지 — 쇼핑 상품(상위 80) 수집 요청을 받는다(서버는 418 차단). 로컬 개발 주소 포함",
      "matches": [
        "https://rankfree.kr/admin/*",
        "https://*.rankfree.co.kr/admin/*",
        "http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/*",
        "http://localhost:8000/admin/*"
      ],
      "js": ["content/admin-bridge.js"],
      "run_at": "document_idle"
    },
    {
      "comment": "쇼핑 노출 키워드 ↔ 확장 브릿지 — 순위체크용 m.search HTML·상품정보를 브라우저에서 대신 가져온다(서버는 IP 한도). 2026-07-21 콘솔→관리자 이동(구 console 경로는 배포 전 prod 호환용 유지)",
      "matches": [
        "https://rankfree.kr/admin/shop-keyword*",
        "https://*.rankfree.co.kr/admin/shop-keyword*",
        "http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/shop-keyword*",
        "http://localhost:8000/admin/shop-keyword*",
        "https://rankfree.kr/console/shop-keyword*",
        "http://127.0.0.1:8000/console/shop-keyword*",
        "http://localhost:8000/console/shop-keyword*"
      ],
      "js": ["content/console-bridge.js"],
      "run_at": "document_idle"
    },
    {
      "matches": ["https://shopping.naver.com/popup/seller-info/*"],
      "js": ["content/seller-info-captcha-injected.js"],
      "world": "MAIN",
      "run_at": "document_start"
    },
    {
      "matches": ["https://shopping.naver.com/popup/seller-info/*"],
      "js": ["content/seller-info-captcha.js"],
      "run_at": "document_idle"
    },
    {
      "matches": ["https://search.naver.com/search.naver*"],
      "js": ["content/content.js"],
      "css": ["content/panel.css", "content/seller-power.css"],
      "run_at": "document_idle"
    },
    {
      "matches": ["https://map.naver.com/*"],
      "js": ["content/content.js"],
      "css": ["content/panel.css", "content/seller-power.css"],
      "run_at": "document_idle"
    },
    {
      "matches": [
        "https://smartstore.naver.com/*/products/*",
        "https://brand.naver.com/*/products/*"
      ],
      "js": ["content/injected-store.js"],
      "world": "MAIN",
      "run_at": "document_start"
    },
    {
      "matches": [
        "https://smartstore.naver.com/*/products/*",
        "https://brand.naver.com/*/products/*"
      ],
      "js": ["content/product.js"],
      "css": ["content/panel.css", "content/seller-power.css"],
      "run_at": "document_idle"
    },
    {
      "matches": ["https://pcmap.place.naver.com/*"],
      "all_frames": true,
      "js": ["content/place-rank.js"],
      "css": ["content/place-rank.css"],
      "run_at": "document_idle"
    }
  ],
  "action": {
    "default_title": "RankFree 분석",
    "default_icon": {
      "16": "icons/icon16.png",
      "48": "icons/icon48.png",
      "128": "icons/icon128.png"
    }
  }
}
